  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Temp Logistics Assistant (3 Month Contract)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>In charge of verifying shipment content against shipping documents provided.</li><li>Responsible in assisting in material picking against pick list and packing of outbound shipments.</li><li>In charge of rejecting damage items and record discrepancies.</li><li>In charge of data entry into ERP system.</li><li>Responsible in assisting Logistics Officer in coordinating with logistics provider on shipment collection.</li><li>In Charge of the visual inspect material for defects and report these and any unusual situation immediately.</li><li>Operate lift trucks, hand trucks, forklifts, stackers, or any other lifting or material handling equipment/devices to move, convey, or hoist materials or products, following the training provided.</li><li>Maintain good housekeeping practices in work area.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Min GCE ‘O’ level and above</li><li>Min 3 year of experience in ERP systems, lifting devices and Material Handling Equipment (MHE).</li><li>Possess a Class 3 Driving License and Forklift License.</li></ul><p>To submit your application, please apply online <a href=\"mailto:apply@rn-care.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>apply@rn-care.com</strong></a><strong> </strong>or call<strong> </strong><a href=\"tel:+(65)%C2%A06513 5697\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>+(65) 6513 5697</strong></a> for private and confidential discussion.</p><p>Your interest will be treated with the strictest of confidence. We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified or contacted.</p><p><strong>RN Care Pte. Ltd</strong><br /><strong>EA License No: 17C8900</strong></p>",
